  "text": "The PDFs are the fundamental object that xFitter works with, and it has a variety of utilities to read, write, and manipulate the PDFs and associated uncertainties. For example, xFitter is able to read and write PDFs in the LHAPDF6 format [CITATION_1] , and Fig. 2 illustrates a sample plot of the PDFs from various global fitting projects.",
